{"tid":1565504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國中央政法委批評李嘉誠縱容犯罪","createTime":"2019-09-13T07:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:52:42.000Z","uid":125193,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c1a8a9abbe8f36391ac35e086a4285e7c98ef0","tid":1565504,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:29:43.000Z","msg":"長和資深顧問李嘉誠日前表示，政府應該對未來的主人翁網開一面。中央政法委在微博公眾號貼文，批評李嘉誠縱容犯罪，不是為香港著想，而是看著香港滑向深淵。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，在目前的香港亂局中，不少年輕人將樓價高、租金貴的憤怒，發洩到政府的頭上，但認為他們可能搞錯了發洩對象，又強調香港並不是沒有地，但發展總會遇到反對聲音，香港樓宇的天價對誰人有利，答案不難猜測，反問李嘉誠等「囤地圈錢」的地產商，會否對市民及香港的未來網開一面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480369-20190913.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480369-20190913.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4Qd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=1732afea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480369-20190913.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9e759e19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480369-20190913.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"88e1aaf56c1e862499658879ea35fe0f03c8a6ac","tid":1565504,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB/TG搵我地香港自由之書阿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a h